9. O-O a6 10. Bxc6 { Can only cause trouble for White. } 10... bxc6 11. Re1 c5
{ Whenever White pushes d4, they will weaken their e4-pawn and open up the position for Black's pair of bishops. However, with limited other options, Black's chances are better. }
