{ 12.Nd3  is bad given  12...c5  , where the position will open even more for bishops. }
12. Re1 Qxe5 { A cool sacrifice! } 13. dxe5 Nxf2
{ White isn't able to escape the perpetual check. } 14. Qf3 Nh3+ 15. Kh1 Nf2+
{ With a perpetual. } *

