12. Qh5
{ A typical queen maneuver, meant to make our king feels uncomfortable. } 12...
c6 13. Ba4 dxe4 14. dxe4 Bxf5
{ Eliminating White's most active piece - the knight.  15.Qxf5  would be met by  15...a5  , with the threat of trapping White's bishop by means of b5, a4. }
