{ As the f2-square is protected by White's queen,  6...Qd4  would be met with the same  7.Nd3  . }
7. Nd3 { The problem is the bishop on c5 which will be hanging now. } 7... Nxe4
{ Black didn't have a great choice - if not taking on e4, we'd simply be a pawn down with no compensation whatsoever. The text move is even worse, as it drops a full piece. }
